670
00:37:14,031 --> 00:37:17,768
I'm filing a 1028 application
to return the minor to her parents.

671
00:37:17,768 --> 00:37:21,138
- Fine. I'll hear that right now.
- Your Honor, we feel that...

672
00:37:21,138 --> 00:37:22,840
I'm gravely distressed by the fact...

673
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:25,910
that police bypassed this court
and took the extreme measure...

