675
00:37:27,678 --> 00:37:30,414
You Honor, the minor has
a chronic history of self-injurious...

676
00:37:30,414 --> 00:37:32,750
behavior casually linked
to the home situation...

677
00:37:32,750 --> 00:37:36,621
Save it for later.
I promise we won't forget about you.

678
00:37:36,621 --> 00:37:39,023
Mr. Woodrow, you're up.

679
00:37:39,023 --> 00:37:42,193
I call Ricki Austin.

680
00:37:42,193 --> 00:37:44,228
We were dirt poor...

681
00:37:44,228 --> 00:37:46,197
so I always swore
that if I made any money...

682
00:37:46,197 --> 00:37:49,000
I was gonna spend all
of it on my children.

683
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:52,169
I wanted them to have
everything they ever wanted.

684
00:37:52,169 --> 00:37:54,972
- Everything I never had.
- In order to do that...

685
00:37:54,972 --> 00:37:57,742
you've been very driven
in your career, haven't you?

686
00:37:57,742 --> 00:38:00,444
I'm a workaholic. I admit it.

687
00:38:00,444 --> 00:38:02,647
Has that kept you from
loving your daughter?

688
00:38:02,647 --> 00:38:05,816
No.

689
00:38:05,816 --> 00:38:08,586
Ashley was my miracle baby.

690
00:38:08,586 --> 00:38:13,624
My first song to become number one,
was about her birth.

691
00:38:13,624 --> 00:38:17,762
Sixteen million people could
relate to a mother's love.

692
00:38:17,762 --> 00:38:20,931
- Is that domestic or worldwide?
- Your Honor...

693
00:38:20,931 --> 00:38:25,777
We have contempt charges here
in family court also, Miss Cabot.

694
00:38:25,777 --> 00:38:27,705
The woman who started
these proceedings...

695
00:38:27,705 --> 00:38:32,476
Detective Benson. / How did she
become involved in your life?

696
00:38:32,476 --> 00:38:35,980
When I lost my son, Corbin...

697
00:38:35,980 --> 00:38:39,183
I was out of my mind with grief.

698
00:38:39,183 --> 00:38:41,652
I was convinced that a man
had been hurting him...

699
00:38:41,652 --> 00:38:44,922
and she was one of the detectives
assigned to the case.

700
00:38:44,922 --> 00:38:46,824
And during the investigation...

701
00:38:46,824 --> 00:38:50,394
did it become necessary
to take out a restraining order?

702
00:38:50,394 --> 00:38:52,830
- Objection.
- Overruled.

703
00:38:52,830 --> 00:38:59,028
I had to. Det. Benson became
obsessed with Ashley.

704
00:39:00,104 --> 00:39:02,306
Miss Austin, did you
ever grow concerned...

705
00:39:02,306 --> 00:39:05,710
over the inordinate number
of injuries your daughter has?

706
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:10,915
Ashley's full of life.
It's hard to contain that energy.

707
00:39:10,915 --> 00:39:13,951
I mean, all kids have accidents.
I know I always did.

708
00:39:13,951 --> 00:39:17,221
Kids will be kids.

709
00:39:17,221 --> 00:39:21,392
On July 13, 1996,
Ashley sprained her wrist.

710
00:39:21,392 --> 00:39:23,794
Where were you?

711
00:39:23,794 --> 00:39:26,464
I... It was a long time ago, I know.

712
00:39:26,464 --> 00:39:27,565
Maybe this will help.

713
00:39:27,565 --> 00:39:31,804
It's your tour schedule
for the last five years.

714
00:39:34,605 --> 00:39:37,341
I gave a concert in Chicago.

715
00:39:37,341 --> 00:39:43,414
And on December 9, 1997?

716
00:39:43,414 --> 00:39:46,317
The German leg of
my European tour.

717
00:39:46,317 --> 00:39:49,653
Also the date Ashley
dislocated her elbow.

718
00:39:49,653 --> 00:39:54,058
Where were you for
her multiple rib fractures?

719
00:39:54,058 --> 00:39:58,062
- What date is that?
- Dates. I said multiple.

720
00:39:58,062 --> 00:40:02,700
March 23, 1998,
August 9, 1999. / Stop it.

721
00:40:02,700 --> 00:40:06,707
There are also lacerations to the upper
and lower extremities. / Objection.

722
00:40:06,707 --> 00:40:09,883
A periorbital fracture,
various foreign bodies lodged

723
00:40:09,883 --> 00:40:12,444
- in her ears...a fractured left femur.
- Stop it.

724
00:40:12,444 --> 00:40:15,713
Objection! / Contusions and abrasions
to the forehead,  chin, hands and knees.

725
00:40:15,713 --> 00:40:18,959
That's enough, Miss Cabot.

726
00:40:20,284 --> 00:40:23,754
All of these injuries correlate
to dates you were away.

727
00:40:23,754 --> 00:40:29,226
You never saw them as a desperate
cry for Mommy to come home?

728
00:40:29,226 --> 00:40:32,296
I love my daughter.

729
00:40:32,296 --> 00:40:36,333
I loved both of my children.

730
00:40:36,333 --> 00:40:38,636
I gave them the best of everything.

731
00:40:38,636 --> 00:40:44,141
The best schools, the best nannies,
the best home.

732
00:40:44,141 --> 00:40:48,039
I did everything I could for them.

733
00:40:50,748 --> 00:40:55,186
No further questions.

734
00:40:55,186 --> 00:40:59,723
You may step down, Miss Austin.

735
00:40:59,723 --> 00:41:03,386
Bailiff, bring in the child.

736
00:41:12,169 --> 00:41:17,074
- Hello, Ashley.
- Hi.

737
00:41:17,074 --> 00:41:21,579
Do you know why
you're here today?

738
00:41:21,579 --> 00:41:27,051
- Do you know Det. Benson?
- She used to be my friend.

739
00:41:27,051 --> 00:41:33,457
- "Used to be?"
- I wanted to live with her.

740
00:41:33,457 --> 00:41:36,660
But she didn't want me.

741
00:41:36,660 --> 00:41:40,937
My daddy's home.

742
00:41:52,309 --> 00:41:55,946
I am ordering the minor
be returned to her parents.

743
00:41:55,946 --> 00:41:59,583
But the Article 10 will continue.
I am recommending that ACS...

744
00:41:59,583 --> 00:42:02,820
monitor the home,
and set up family counseling.

745
00:42:02,820 --> 00:42:05,389
I want a status report
in one month.

746
00:42:05,389 --> 00:42:07,124
There won't be much to report,
Your Honor...

747
00:42:07,124 --> 00:42:09,260
because she begins
a three-month tour next week...

748
00:42:09,260 --> 00:42:12,563
and her daughter needs
to be in school. / Ms. Austin?

749
00:42:12,563 --> 00:42:18,023
- I'll postpone that tour, Your Honor.
- Wise decision.

750
00:42:25,409 --> 00:42:29,013
I want you to know that
my only concern was for Ashley.

751
00:42:29,013 --> 00:42:34,873
You ever get near her again,
I'll have your badge.

752
00:42:35,853 --> 00:42:38,050
Gorgeous!

753
00:42:50,634 --> 00:42:53,103
How is it out there
in the real world?

754
00:42:53,103 --> 00:42:56,106
Give him a few more days
to cool off.

755
00:42:56,106 --> 00:42:58,208
He'll let you off ass-duty.

756
00:42:58,208 --> 00:43:01,512
Just in time for my hearing
in front of the disciplinary committee.

757
00:43:01,512 --> 00:43:05,549
- I see them next week.
- Was it worth it?

758
00:43:05,549 --> 00:43:10,935
I don't know.
I think it woke her up.

759
00:43:21,031 --> 00:43:25,436
- Son of a bitch.
- What?

760
00:43:25,436 --> 00:43:31,101
Ricki Austin played to a sold-out crowd
in London last night.

